": \"SALT LAKE CITY - The last time Utah hosted the Winter Olympics, things looked a little different.\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 544, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"score\": 0.9999824299283916, \"rank\": 1.3515864925949018e-05, \"text\": \"SALT LAKE CITY\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\"}, {\"begin\": 544, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"score\": 0.9999824299283916, \"rank\": 1.3515864925949018e-05, \"text\": \"SALT LAKE CITY\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\"}, {\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9995260701745293, \"rank\": 0.000474123313880532, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Winter Olympics\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No, we are not just talking about hairstyles or fashion trends.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hairstyles\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"fashion trends\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back then, there were not nearly as many of us.\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have added about 1.2 million more people since 2002,\\\" said Natalie Gochnour, who directs the Kem C. Gardner Policy Institute at the University of Utah.\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 860, \"end\": 867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L._Gardner_and_Sons\", \"score\": 0.7982490664449761, \"rank\": 0.25274183463803657, \"text\": \"Gardner\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L._Gardner_and_Sons\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L._Gardner_and_Sons\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about 1.2 million more people\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"Natalie Gochnour\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 902}, {\"ngram\": \"Utah\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's about the size of Salt Lake County today.\\\"\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_County,_Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999999729425, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Salt Lake County\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_County,_Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_County,_Utah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the size\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gochnour said that growth has led to many changes for our once-small state.\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gochnour\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 972}, {\"ngram\": \"growth\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 989}, {\"ngram\": \"many changes\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"our once-small state\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1038}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have become a larger economy,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a larger economy\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"More international trade, more international engagement.\\\"\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"More international trade\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \", more international engagement\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today Utah acts much bigger.\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1152, \"end\": 1156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9995260701745293, \"rank\": 0.000474123313880532, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Take Salt Lake City, for example.\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1180, \"end\": 1194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"score\": 0.9999817423306551, \"rank\": 1.3515864925949018e-05, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In 2002, we did not have downtown urban living.\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"downtown urban living\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We had a city that closed at 6:00, 7:00 at night,\\\" said Gochnour.\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a city\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1307}, {\"ngram\": \"Gochnour\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now it's much more of a 24/7 city.\\\"\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1361, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 24/7 city\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's also a city that now has a convention hotel, a Broadway theater, a busy downtown mall, and a brand new international airport.\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1493, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a city\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1379}, {\"ngram\": \"a convention hotel\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"a Broadway theater\"