verse.\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our state\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2002, one in 10 Utahns were an ethnic or racial minority, Gochnour said.\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2215, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"10 Utahns\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2165}, {\"ngram\": \"an ethnic or racial minority\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"Gochnour\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By the time the 2034 Games roll around, it will be nearly one in three.\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a lot to do to get ready over the next decade.\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2303}, {\"ngram\": \"the next decade\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Gochnour said it's work that needs to be done anyway to keep up with a state that's changing quickly.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gochnour\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2357}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2372}, {\"ngram\": \"a state\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you are going to be host to the world, you get better in every way,\\\" said Gochnour.\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"host\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"every way\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2524}, {\"ngram\": \"Gochnour\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think of the Olympics more as a motivator for the good things we can do for growth that's coming no matter what.\\\"\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 255